But I don’t want you to go.

41
00:04:43,630 --> 00:04:44,720
It's fine.

42
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,360
I’m just leaving the manor,

43
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,800
not the Silver City.

44
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,430
If you miss me,

45
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
go to the Southern City to visit me.

46
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,950
Master Long, you know

47
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,630
the Silk Manor and Longzhu Gang

48
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,830
never have any dealings usually.

49
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,360
Separated by a wall,

50
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:59,190
we seem to be hundreds of miles
away from each other.

51
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,040
Yes, that’s right.

52
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,600
We’re busy working on weekdays.

53
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,830
Even our master

54
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,270
rarely goes out of the manor.

55
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,630
I don’t want to see him.

56
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:09,920
A lot of things have happened recently.

57
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,160
I haven’t gone out

58
