for months.

59
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,830
It’s okay. At the worst,

60
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:15,360
I can dig a doghole

61
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,920
in the corner for each of you.

62
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:17,920
Everyone owns a door.

63
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:19,270
I will receive you personally.

64
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,310
Well, don’t be upset.

65
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,310
We have a celebration party tonight.

66
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,120
All right then.

67
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:37,660
= Xinsilu =

68
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,510
The gold thread was recovered.

69
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,040
Their business starts to run again.

70
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,750
The money I’ve invested

71
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,360
should be recouped with interest.

72
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:49,120
But Dongzi is dead.

73
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:50,560
Who is the accountant now?

74
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,040
Second Master.

75
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,510
Master, we know
you’re leaving the manor today.

76
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,560
We’ve already prepared a banquet.

77
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,390
A brazier.

78
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,870
First, to wash you off the dust.

79
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,630
Second, to help you
out of the ill-fortune.

80
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:04,920
We got everything prepared.

81
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,070
We must celebrate after we return.

82
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:08,600
Of course we must celebrate.

83
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,920
First, we cleared the Longzhu Gang

84
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:13,160
of suspicion about the gold thread,

85
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,040
and recovered Dachun’s reputation.

86
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,070
Second,

87
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:18,750
I can finally leave the terrible place.

88
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,190
There’s one more thing to celebrate.

89
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:24,070
The money our brothers saved

90
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,720
has earned lots of interest.

91
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,390
Master Li.

92
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:35,310
Don’t rush me.

93
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,560
I’ll go as soon as
I get my silver reward.

94
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,160
Happy to work together.

95
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:40,680
Let’s have an amicable parting,
and never meet again.

96
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,160
You can’t go.

97
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,270
What do you want, Li Qingliu?

98
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,360
Are you trying to deny?

99
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,750
I don’t owe anyone favors.

100
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:52,270
Manager Liu is out on business today.

101
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,870
I must pay you the reward tomorrow.

102
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:58,160
He is out. Fine.

103
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,950
I’m not in a hurry.

104
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,800
I’ll come back another day.

105
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,950
Second Master. Let’s go.

106
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,040
Wait!

107
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,950
Not only you and me

108
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,800
suffered from the gold thread incident,

109
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,390
but the whole Silk Manor

110
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,160
suffered too.

111
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,560
So?

112
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,160
So I want to take this opportunity

113
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,160
to give everyone a vacation.

114
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,270
Let’s relax a little.

115
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,390
You, Second Master and Xiaoqin,

116
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,750
are all invited.

117
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:23,560
Master,

118
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:26,510
I think Master Li is sincere.

119
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:27,830
It’s difficult to refuse such kindness.

120
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,390
Why don't you let our brothers

121
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:31,040
take two days off for relaxation?

122
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:37,270
OK. Well.

123
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,240
Shall we have a meal?

124
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:40,750
Oh, no, no.

125
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:43,560
You have too bad tastes.
It’s boring to have a meal with you.

126
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:44,830
Then an opera?

127
00:07:45,070 --> 00:07:45,750
No.

128
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,190
Handsome scholars and pretty girls.

129
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,160
Emperors and generals. They’re insipid.

130
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,240
Well, forget it.

131
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,480
I’d better go back to eat meat.

132
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:00,950
Master,

133
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,600
