134
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,240
That sounds nice.

135
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:09,870
It’s relaxing.

136
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:12,390
At the foot of the mountain
in the south of the city,

137
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,720
I’m running a hot spring.

138
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:15,750
Such a nice coincidence.

139
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,070
Suitable for young and old.

140
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,480
It's settled then.

141
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:24,000
Well, it's just two or three days.

142
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,070
The Silk Manor won’t be stolen.

143
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,870
That’s it. I have to go.

144
