147
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:45,120
and maintains regular production.

148
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:47,080
He doesn’t lack goods and funds.

149
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:48,790
I thought

150
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,480
as long as we cut off his supply,

151
