155
00:08:57,480 --> 00:09:00,240
He even got back on his feet
after having recovered the gold thread.

156
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,870
By contrast,

157
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,240
the interest we have to pay this month

158
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,630
