163
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,030
Go for wool and come home shorn.

164
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:17,480
At last, we are the one

165
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:19,030
who is in a dilemma.

166
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:27,200
Your Highness.

167
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,750
Your Highness. The bosses

168
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,080
