in person.

169
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,480
I have it counted.

170
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:38,200
That's the total.

171
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,790
Well, about the selection of guild leader,

172
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:49,440
Your Highness, with all due respect,

173
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:51,510
It’s an open secret in the guild.

174
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,320
Shen Yiguan

175
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,600
isn’t open to persuasion,

176
