The imperial court presented

182
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,240
gold and silver to him.

183
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,840
He refused to take it.

184
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,440
Instead, he stretched his arm

185
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:09,480
to the south to earn hard money.

186
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,000
With so many efforts,

187
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,200
did he try to avoid something?

188
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:17,240
Now, Li Qingliu is encumbered

189
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,240
by the production
of gold thread clothes.

190
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,630
But he still turned down
the offer of the government.

191
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,510
He is really in contempt
of the imperial court.

192
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,200
Don't mention him again.

193
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,840
I specially prepared good liquor
for Your Highness.

194
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,720
Your Highness, please take your seat.

195
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:31,750
I appreciate your kind offer.

196
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:32,790
Mr. Du,

197
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,240
please send several tax officials

198
00:10:36,150 --> 00:10:38,150
to Xinsilu tomorrow.

199
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,960
Goodbye, Your Highness.

