00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:44,780
= Suyong Hall =

201
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,080
Your Highness, when you first
came to Silver City,

202
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:56,550
the servants

203
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,360
presented you
with the account book of Xinsilu.

204
00:10:58,790 --> 00:10:59,960
There seemed to be no problem.

205
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,030
Did you see the wily old birds?

206
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,200
They want to use my sword
to fight their own battle.

207
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:06,390
Good.

208
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:07,910
I’ll push the boat with the current.

209
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,030
Maybe,

210
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:11,150
I would catch the foxes’ tails.

211
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,030
As for Li Qingliu,

212
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,840
he needs to be put in his place.

213
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,440
Before Sister came here,

214
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,750
master never let us come out with him

215
00:11:42,750 --> 00:11:44,390
and have group activities.

216
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,550
It’s nothing.

217
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,030
In Longzhu Gang,

218
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,080
we usually go out together

219
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,390
to wine and dine.

220
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,550
Your master

221
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,440
doesn’t know how to use
the “prison and rabbit” tactic.

222
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:54,910
Prison and rabbit?

223
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:56,030
Yeah.

224
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:58,390
Make you work like you are in prison.

225
00:11:58,750 --> 00:12:00,030
Sometimes let you out

226
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,080
and jump at will like rabbits.

227
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,150
He is so stingy.

228
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:17,600
Master Li looks young,

229
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,550
but you’re running
such a big family business.

230
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,120
You’re competent.

231
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,030
I’m flattered.

232
00:12:26,270 --> 00:12:27,320
With all due respect,

233
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,630
how old are you?

234
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,720
I was adopted by the Li Family
when I was a child.

235
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,910
It was probably in Shangyuan Period.

236
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:38,200
Shangyuan Period?

237
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:44,150
Freshly boiled hotspring eggs!

238
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:50,790
Master!

239
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:52,550
When shall we go back to the gang?

240
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:55,150
Soon. In the future,

241
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:55,870
we don’t have to see

242
00:12:55,910 --> 00:12:57,630
the stink face again.

243
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,790
But after spending these days with him,

244
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:01,840
I don’t think Master Li

245
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,030
is a bad person.

246
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,440
Just think, he is a profiteer,

247
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,550
but he didn’t go after the gold thread.

248
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:08,580
Instead, he went to save you.

249
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:10,550
Come on.

250
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,360
I was so lucky

251
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,550
that he didn’t break my bones.

252
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:20,670
Master.

253
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:23,120
How much money do we get?

254
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:27,000
I did the math.

255
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,440
With the 10,000 taels of silver reward,

256
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:32,790
we get 80,000 taels of silver in total.

257
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:35,750
That's enough for us
to open a few more stores,

258
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,120
and purchase a few more mu of land
for silkworm rearing.

259
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,200
One is enough.

260
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,360
No one will marry you if you get fat.

261
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:56,440
Wait for me for a moment.

262
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:05,440
Master.

263
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,270
It’s a nice place.

264
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,390
Shuisheng and Qi Zheng are happy.

265
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,910
They were grateful to Master Long.

266
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,480
Two men have a bath together.

267
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,270
Never mind.

268
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,120
If I may say,

269
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:28,550
you have a different attitude
toward Master Long.

270
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,630
See,

271
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,790
Silk Manor never welcomes outsiders.

272
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,320
She is the first.

273
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,320
All the clerks take a vacation.

274
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:41,670
It hasn’t been heard of for years.

275
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,120
You don’t want to be close to women.

276
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,320
You even keep the right distance
to Miss Du.

277
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:48,390
But, these days,

278
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,390
